@startuml
title Delete Process (Level 1) — VendNet

actor "Actor\n(Operator/Admin)" as User
participant "VendNet System" as System

User -> System: Request Deletion (ID)
activate System
System -> System: Validate & Process Deletion
alt Deletion Successful
    System --> User: Display Success Message
else Deletion Failed / Not Found
    System --> User: Display Error Message
end
deactivate System
@enduml